0) make
1) go to the test directory:
    cd test
2) generate 3000 random values to the numbers.txt file:
    g++ -std=c++11 numbers_generator.cpp -o numbers_generator
    ./numbers_generator > numbers.txt
3) sort:
    cat numbers.txt | xargs ../PmergeMe > sorted.txt
4) check:
    g++ -std=c++11 sort_checker.cpp -o sort_checker
    ./sort_checker


